description: **Non-Owner Occupied Short Term Rental, NOO STR, Airbnb/VRBO allowed**  Top performing STR with almost $80k annual projections and almost $20k in May & June this year alone!  Super rare 2 bed/2 full bath top floor Riverfront unit.  Unbeatable location overlooking the Cumberland River just steps away from famous Broadway, Horizon Park, the *new* Nissan Stadium, Ascend Amphitheater, Bridgestone Arena and more!  Professionally decorated by Crystal Beckel of Avalon Blue Home for the fellow Swiftie lover and one that makes the scrollers STOP.  Brand new furniture negotiable and new LVP flooring throughout.  Community amenities include pool, fitness center, laundry facilities, outdoor area with firepit and covered parking.  Proforma available upon request.  Buyer/Buyer's agent to verify all pertinent information.
